{'en': {'shortDesc': 'Enterprise Resource Management (client)', 'pkgName': 'openerp-client', 'longDesc': u'Open ERP, previously known as TinyERP, is a complete ERP and CRM. The main features are accounting (analytic and financial), stock management, sales and purchases management, tasks automation, marketing campaigns, help desk, POS, etc. Technical features include a distributed server, flexible workflows, an object database, a dynamic GUI, customizable reports, and NET-RPC and XML-RPC interfaces.\n\nThis package contains the Open ERP client, install openerp-server package for the server.'}}